productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Alida has one of these. She works as a gambler and she says it looks spotless.
heard about this on gypsy jazz radio, decided to give it a try.
This Comoro Franc works very well. It harmonically improves my tennis by a lot.
My scarab beetle loves to play with it.
one of my hobbies is poetry. and when i'm writing poems this works great.
